eu.cqse.check.framework.util.python

Class PythonVariableNameExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.util.python.PythonVariableNameExtractor

  • public class PythonVariableNameExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that extracts declared variable names from shallow entities in python. Currently extraction is implemented for.
    • expect statements
    • for statements
    • with statements
    • method parameters
    • lambda parameters
    • variable and attribute declarations (with destructuring)

    For loops within list comprehensions are currently not supported.
